  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13076885/japan_intro_m19-1.jpg? alt=" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/e1f1344e5a3c4c9abc87e3741ea100a4" /></p>
<p>Everyone's been talking about the incredible skiing, so we went there to find out ourselves. You'll be happy to know the rumours are true, and we can prove it with two amazing ski resorts-<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/japan/hakuba" title="Hakuba">Hakuba</a><span> </span>and<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/japan/nozawa-onsen" title="Nozawa Onsen">Nozawa Onsen</a>.</p>
<p><em>Our holidays to Japan include the following:</em></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Free Lift Passes</strong>- included in all holidays</li>
<li><strong>Flexible Itineraries</strong>- enjoy the ski then add on a city break in either Tokyo or Kyoto</li>
<li><strong>Transfers and Meet &amp; Greet</strong> - included in all holidays</li>
<li><strong>Bed &amp; Breakfast Basis</strong>- in all hotels</li>
<li><strong>Free ski carriage</strong>- using our preferred supplier, Japan Airlines</li>
</ul>
<p>Online you will find a selection of pre-packaged itineraries for a 5 or 7 night break to Japan. Alternatively, call and speak to a member of our specialist Reservations Team, some of whom have visited these destinations to provide you with your very own tailored itinerary and visit up to 28 nights.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1c75c362696e43cfabf9211c412d2cd1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1c75c362696e43cfabf9211c412d2cd1}" title="Japan">Japan</a> is where you can combine ski holidays with fascinating cultural experiences- lose yourself in the dizzy heights of<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/c7af808018e443518d3f725c12321904" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/japan/tokyo" title="Tokyo">Tokyo</a><span> </span>and feast on traditional cuisine, visit the temples in<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/25c2fbfd78524b50b0b912ebb152521c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/japan/kyoto" title="Kyoto">Kyoto</a><span> </span>or pay respects in Hiroshima, spot the Snow Monkeys at the mountain Onsen and then relax in the thermal waters of Nozawa or ski 10 resorts in Hakuba, sip sake and experience the bullet train back to Tokyo.</p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
