<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Tokyo &amp; Hakuba</h3>
<p><img style="width: 400px; height: 214px;" src="/media/13076886/hakuba_intro_m19-1.jpg?width=400&amp;height=214&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5128e3ed5d9243daaa6d3d4e23d1f7f6" /></p>
<p><strong>Hunt for 'japow'!</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Spend your first and last night in Tokyo</li>
<li>Book a 3 or 5 night stay in Hakuba online or call us for a longer stay</li>
<li>Hakuba is home to 10 ski resorts on 1 lift pass</li>
<li>Accommodation in Happo One</li>
<li>Extend your stay with 2 nights in Kyoto</li>
</ul>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d}" title="Hakuba">Find out more &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Tokyo &amp; Nozawa</h3>
<p><img style="width: 401px; height: 215px;" src="/media/13075560/nozawa-2.jpg?width=401&amp;height=215&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a93bc1a8e5714e1e8109e1506183ce01" /></p>
<p><strong>From city to ski</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Spend your first and last night in Tokyo</li>
<li>Book a 3 or 5 night stay in Nozawa Onsen online or call us for a longer stay</li>
<li>Traditional Onsen village with excursions available to visit the Snow Monkeys</li>
<li>Brand new gondola from resort to mountain</li>
<li>Extend your stay with 2 nights in Kyoto</li>
</ul>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1}" title="Nozawa Onsen">Find out more &gt;</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Additional City Stopovers</h3>
<p>Why not add a little extra to your stay in Japan. Travelling long haul, you'll want to make it count, so on your return you can choose between an additional night or two in Tokyo or why not visit Kyoto?</p>
<p>Rich in culture and history, the old capital of <em>Kyoto</em> is a must see for any traveller searching for an authentic Japanese stay.</p>
<ul>
<li>Extend your Tokyo &amp; Hakuba or your Tokyo &amp; Nozawa package with 2 nights in Kyoto</li>
<li>Kyoto city hotel situated next to the train station</li>
<li>Visit Buddhist temples, Shinto shrines and spot a Geisha</li>
<li>Find out more by visiting <a data-udi="umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d}" title="Hakuba">Tokyo &amp; Hakuba</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1}" title="Nozawa Onsen">Tokyo &amp; Nozawa</a></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
